summary: Enables Fast Travel from indoor areas
descriptionHtml:
[b][size=5]Fast Travel From Indoors[/size][/b]  [size=1]WIP[/size]

[color=red]THIS MOD CAN CAUSE CTDs IN CONJUNCTION WITH SOME OTHERS (e.g. W.A.T.E.R.)
YOU CAN DOWNLOAD IT AT YOUR OWN RISK[/color]

[u]Description[/u]

Enables Fast Travel from all indoor areas [b]excluding[/b]:
- All jails
- Sovngarde
- Inside Azuras Star
and some others

[u]Installation instructions[/u]

Extract archive contents into the game\'s root folder and check FastTravelFromIndoors.esp in launcher Data Files or in NMM.

[u]Known issues[/u]

May conflict with mods that modify location cells\' settings

[u]WIP[/u]

Please report any locations where fast travel must not be enabled, but is enabled by this mod.

[b]My new mod[/b]
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=12338]Drem Fah Pah Nahl[/url]
author: Mikanoshi
